00:02:02,700 --> 00:02:05,380
=Episode 1=
(Please Make a Pact with Me)

19
00:02:05,920 --> 00:02:08,800
(Mu Residence)
Traitor Mu Heng betrayed

20
00:02:08,840 --> 00:02:10,040
Emperor's abundant grace.

21
00:02:10,240 --> 00:02:11,480
After Lord Yi's investigation,

22
00:02:11,600 --> 00:02:13,280
it was found

23
00:02:13,480 --> 00:02:15,080
that Mu Heng had plotted rebellion.

24
00:02:15,160 --> 00:02:16,360
His ill intent deserves death,

25
00:02:16,520 --> 00:02:17,760
and his behavior is contemptible.

26
00:02:18,120 --> 00:02:20,360
(Master Mu)
Hence, strip him of his title as Grand Tutor at once,

27
00:02:20,440 --> 00:02:21,640
and execute his entire household

28
00:02:21,840 --> 00:02:23,200
without mercy.

29
00:02:25,280 --> 00:02:26,480
Xue, run!

30
00:02:26,600 --> 00:02:27,440
Go that way.

31
00:02:27,840 --> 00:02:28,560
Faster.

32
00:02:29,480 --> 00:02:31,400
No one in the Mu Residence
is to be spared.

33
00:02:31,760 --> 00:02:32,240
Go search.

34
00:02:32,240 --> 00:02:33,040
Hurry up, Xue.

35
00:02:34,520 --> 00:02:35,320
Run.

36
00:02:36,680 --> 00:02:37,200
Mother.

37
00:02:37,400 --> 00:02:38,480
No matter what happens,

38
00:02:38,520 --> 00:02:39,520
don't look back.

39
00:02:40,320 --> 00:02:41,800
(Mu Lingxue)
You must survive.

40
00:02:42,480 --> 00:02:43,760
Go, Xue.

41
00:02:44,000 --> 00:02:44,800
Over there.

42
00:02:45,040 --> 00:02:45,840
Get her.

43
00:02:46,340 --> 00:02:48,180
(Madam Mu)

44
00:02:48,200 --> 00:02:49,000
Mother.

45
00:02:50,360 --> 00:02:51,200
Stand right there.

46
00:02:52,040 --> 00:02:52,680
Over there.

47
00:02:53,160 --> 00:02:54,600
Run, Xue!

48
00:02:57,040 --> 00:02:57,920
Now!

49
00:03:10,960 --> 00:03:12,560
Mother.

50
00:03:18,560 --> 00:03:19,360
Search the room.

51
00:03:23,040 --> 00:03:24,800
Where is she?
There must be a secret passage here.

52
00:03:24,800 --> 00:03:26,160
The lord wants her alive.

53
00:03:26,320 --> 00:03:26,790
Search around.

54
00:03:53,320 --> 00:03:54,640
It's her.

55
00:03:54,640 --> 00:03:55,760
The red-haired woman.

56
00:03:56,000 --> 00:03:57,400
Red hair is an ill omen.

57
00:03:57,600 --> 00:03:58,400
Burn her!

58
