- Burn her!

62
00:04:13,840 --> 00:04:15,280
What are you doing?

63
00:04:15,280 --> 00:04:16,080
Release me.

64
00:04:16,240 --> 00:04:17,840
She broke into the village.

65
00:04:18,080 --> 00:04:20,080
She'll bring disaster on us.

66
00:04:20,080 --> 00:04:22,080
That's right.
She must be a harbinger of doom.

67
00:04:22,120 --> 00:04:22,680
If she stays,

68
00:04:22,920 --> 00:04:24,640
our village will be doomed.

69
00:04:25,280 --> 00:04:27,080
We can't let her stay.

70
00:04:27,520 --> 00:04:28,880
Burn her as tribute to Heaven.

71
