- Burn her!
- Burn her!

87
00:05:19,920 --> 00:05:21,480
Deity! The deity is here.

88
00:05:21,680 --> 00:05:22,480
The deity is here.

89
00:05:22,760 --> 00:05:24,160
- The deity descends!
- The deity descends!

90
00:05:24,320 --> 00:05:26,100
- Greetings, Heavenly Deity!
- Greetings, Heavenly Deity!

91
00:05:26,640 --> 00:05:27,880
(It's the Divine Beast Phoenix.)

92
00:05:28,080 --> 00:05:29,301
(Chi Yu)
(Legend has it that if a human)

93
00:05:29,301 --> 00:05:30,400
(Chi Yu)
makes a pact with a divine beast,)

94
00:05:30,680 --> 00:05:32,440
(the beast will grant one wish.)

95
00:05:32,440 --> 00:05:34,600
Help me.

96
00:05:46,440 --> 00:05:47,480
(Xuanzhu Jade?)

97
00:06:10,600 --> 00:06:12,200
(I'm saved.)

98
00:06:55,200 --> 00:06:56,000
Speak up.

99
00:06:56,480 --> 00:06:57,680
Where is the Xuanzhu Jade?

100
00:06:58,400 --> 00:07:00,080
I don't know any Xuanzhu Jade.

101
00:07:03,557 --> 00:07:06,517
I saw the Xuanzhu Jade on you
with my own eyes.

102
00:07:09,440 --> 00:07:10,720
Don't try to trick me.

103
00:07:11,560 --> 00:07:13,600
I have ways to make you suffer.

104
00:07:14,000 --> 00:07:16,080
If you tell me
where the Xuanzhu Jade is.

105
00:07:16,080 --> 00:07:17,800
I don't know anything about it.

106
00:07:18,440 --> 00:07:19,320
If you don't talk,

107
00:07:20,600 --> 00:07:22,200
you must die.

108
00:07:38,680 --> 00:07:40,320
(Xuanzhu Jade is really inside you.)

109
00:07:42,120 --> 00:07:43,560
You're a Wangshu Vessel.

110
00:07:44,920 --> 00:07:46,880
(I really have the Xuanzhu Jade
inside me?)

111
00:07:47,360 --> 00:07:48,240
(Could this be why)

112
00:07:48,720 --> 00:07:50,920
(I was born with red hair?)

113
00:07:53,000 --> 00:07:54,000
(Great.)

114
00:07:58,920 --> 00:07:59,840
What are you trying to do?

115
00:08:00,040 --> 00:08:01,200
I'll use you as a sacrifice.

116
00:08:01,200 --> 00:08:01,720
Let go.

117
00:08:01,720 --> 00:08:02,880
To save my clan.

118
00:08:06,840 --> 00:08:07,640
(What's going on?)

119
00:08:24,160 --> 00:08:24,960
Impossible.

120
00:08:25,480 --> 00:08:27,040
You clearly have
the Xuanzhu Jade on you.

121
00:08:27,560 --> 00:08:28,640
Why won't it return?

122
00:08:56,000 --> 00:08:57,040
(How come?)

123
00:08:58,440 --> 00:08:59,600
(What is this?)

124
00:09:07,640 --> 00:09:09,480
(All things return to their place.)

125
00:09:09,480 --> 00:09:11,600
(To offer me a heart,)

126
00:09:11,600 --> 00:09:13,640
(it must be a willing sacrifice,)

127
00:09:14,040 --> 00:09:16,040
(so that the jade could return
to its place.)

128
00:09:25,440 --> 00:09:26,480
I can

129
00:09:26,680 --> 00:09:27,800
offer myself willingly.

130
00:09:29,080 --> 00:09:31,120
You want the Xuanzhu Jade
inside my body, don't you?

131
00:09:32,000 --> 00:09:32,920
How about

132
00:09:33,640 --> 00:09:34,840
we make a deal?

133
00:09:36,320 --> 00:09:37,760
Who do you think you are

134
00:09:40,480 --> 00:09:42,280
to bargain with me?

135
00:09:42,760 --> 00:09:44,560
Didn't you just try?

136
00:09:44,880 --> 00:09:46,880
Sacrifice needs my consent.

137
00:09:51,240 --> 00:09:52,520
My entire family was massacred.

138
00:09:53,720 --> 00:09:55,120
I was nearly burnt
in a sacrificial rite.

139
00:09:55,920 --> 00:09:57,200
I will not die in peace

140
00:09:57,200 --> 00:09:58,440
until I avenge them.

141
00:09:59,400 --> 00:10:01,000
If you help me get revenge,

142
00:10:01,440 --> 00:10:02,640
I'll sacrifice myself willingly

143
00:10:02,960 --> 00:10:04,280
and let the Xuanzhu Jade return.

144
00:10:08,280 --> 00:10:10,240
I don't make deals with lowly humans.

145
00:10:35,120 --> 00:10:36,120
Mu Lingxue.

146
00:10:37,400 --> 00:10:38,800
Even if you have to kneel,

147
00:10:40,280 --> 00:10:42,080
you must survive.

148
00:10:52,820 --> 00:10:56,300
(On the full moon night, human and deity
combine to make a Twin-soul Contract.)

149
00:11:11,200 --> 00:11:12,240
(Please)

150
00:11:14,000 --> 00:11:15,440
(make a pact with me.)

151
00:11:19,820 --> 00:11:22,380
=Twin Fates=
=End of Episode 1=

152
00:11:23,620 --> 00:11:27,540
♪In a world of sorrows,
every encounter is fleeting♪

153
00:11:29,540 --> 00:11:33,420
♪Life is short
but slumber is long on Penglai Island♪

154
00:11:35,420 --> 00:11:39,940
♪In dreams, mountains and flowers are
as beautiful as jade♪

155
00:11:41,180 --> 00:11:45,220
♪All I ever wish for
is an old friend's return♪

156
00:11:47,180 --> 00:11:51,020
♪Majestic as a soaring dragon,
veiling the sun with drifting clouds♪

157
00:11:52,942 --> 00:11:56,702
♪Graceful as a flying swan goose,
breaking through snow and peril♪

158
00:11:58,860 --> 00:12:03,740
♪Twenty years forsaken,
I lived the life of an outlaw♪

159
00:12:04,580 --> 00:12:08,420
♪On the Ximo River,
who was left behind?♪

160
00:12:08,900 --> 00:12:14,780
♪Bit by bit,
reality shatters my only hope♪

161
00:12:15,300 --> 00:12:20,620
♪Layer by layer, cold blades roll up
the light I once glimpsed in secret♪

162
00:12:20,620 --> 00:12:23,420
♪Letters have long since yellowed♪

163
00:12:23,780 --> 00:12:27,180
♪Leaving only two lonely lines♪

164
00:12:28,100 --> 00:12:32,540
♪Even the old yard is covered
with frost♪

165
00:12:32,540 --> 00:12:37,460
♪Pair after pair,
swallows draw my envious gaze♪

166
00:12:38,540 --> 00:12:44,220
♪Scene after scene,
in dreams I cannot reach♪

167
00:12:44,220 --> 00:12:46,820
♪While you rest beneath the earth♪

168
00:12:46,820 --> 00:12:50,420
♪My love lingers in this frosty world♪

169
00:12:51,220 --> 00:12:59,060
♪How are you now?♪
